title: Muhammad Hamza Shehbaz Sharif wins NA-118 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz Candidate Muhammad Hamza Shehbaz Sharif has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-118 Lahore-II by securing 1,05,960 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Independent candidate Aliya Hamza Malik, who bagged 1,00,803 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 35.83 percent.
